OL,3,CVogue Williams 'nervous' about
OL,4,Cpregnancy after revealing double
OL,5,Cmiscarriage
OL,7,FModel and presenter Vogue Williams has
OL,8,Frevealed she has suffered from
OL,9,F"pregnancy loss" twice.
OL,11,FThe 40-year-old former Heart presenter
OL,12,Fsaid the first happened before the
OL,13,Fbirth of her daughter Gigi in 2020,
OL,14,Fand the second took place last year,
OL,15,Fwhile speaking on her What Does She
OL,16,FEven Do? YouTube channel.
OL,26,@qD@AOUqD@PO]
