OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1776715554
OL,3,CVogue Williams 'nervous' about
OL,4,Cpregnancy after revealing double
OL,5,Cmiscarriage
OL,7,FWilliams and her husband, former Made
OL,8,FIn Chelsea star Spencer Matthews,
OL,9,Fannounced she was pregnant with the
OL,10,Fcouple's fourth child on Thursday. The
OL,11,Fpair currently have three children in
OL,12,FGigi, Otto and Theodore.
OL,14,FShe said: "Trigger warning, pregnancy
OL,15,Floss, if anyone doesn't want to watch,
OL,16,Fdon't.
OL,26,@vD@KOU
