OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1776715554
OL,3,CVogue Williams 'nervous' about
OL,4,Cpregnancy after revealing double
OL,5,Cmiscarriage
OL,7,F"So it happened to me before I had
OL,8,FGigi, not just me, it happened to
OL,9,FSpencer as well obviously, and it was
OL,10,Fso early on, like so, so early on, we
OL,11,Fhadn't had any scans, we hadn't
OL,12,Fanything like that, and I must have
OL,13,Fbeen maybe a month, if even and it was
OL,14,Fjust one of those things.
OL,16,F"And it was awful but everything
OL,17,Fhappened quite quickly after it as
OL,18,Fwell, so I never really kind of
OL,19,Fthought about it much.
OL,26,@oD@AOUxD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1776715554
OL,3,CVogue Williams 'nervous' about
OL,4,Cpregnancy after revealing double
OL,5,Cmiscarriage
OL,7,F"It was really upsetting at the time
OL,8,Fbut then I was pregnant quite quickly
OL,9,Fafter.
OL,11,F"But it actually happened to me last
OL,12,Fyear as well, and it was just, I was
OL,13,Fliterally about to tell the kids...
OL,14,Fyou could kind of start telling I was
OL,15,Fthree months, I just didn't go for an
OL,16,Fearly scan. I just never even thought
OL,17,Fabout it because I kind of didn't want
OL,18,Fto make a fuss."
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@AOUzD@PO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/9
