OL,3,CVogue Williams 'nervous' about
OL,4,Cpregnancy after revealing double
OL,5,Cmiscarriage
OL,7,FWilliams went on to say that she felt
OL,8,F"quite sick" but "not as sick as I
OL,9,Fwould usually feel during pregnancy",
OL,10,Fbefore discovering that "basically the
OL,11,Fembryo hadn't grown".
OL,13,FShe added: "Usually you just naturally
OL,14,Fget a miscarriage, but I didn't, it
OL,15,Fjust kept like it would have
OL,16,Feventually happened, but it just
OL,17,Fdidn't at the time, and I was three
OL,18,Fmonths along, and (the doctor) was
OL,19,Fjust like, I'm really sorry... it's
OL,20,Fnot really a pregnancy."
OL,26,@pD@AOUpD@LO]pD@ROUqD@dO]rD@YOUsD@TO]uD@
OL,26,ALOU|D@XO]
