OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1776715554
OL,3,CVogue Williams 'nervous' about
OL,4,Cpregnancy after revealing double
OL,5,Cmiscarriage
OL,7,F"I'm glad we did, obviously, but now I
OL,8,Fjust have this constant nervousness
OL,9,Faround hoping that everything is going
OL,10,Fto be all right."
OL,12,FThe Irish star announced her latest
OL,13,Fpregnancy with a picture of herself
OL,14,Fwith Matthews, 37, pushing their
OL,15,Fstomachs together in beach attire,
OL,16,Fwhich showed her baby bump, on
OL,17,FInstagram.
OL,26,@oD@AOUrD@QO]
